# http://www.extjs.com/blog/2009/09/30/ext-js-on-rails-a-comprehensivetutorial/
## Install 
    sudo gem install gemcutter
    gem tumble # switch away from github to gemcutter ins ~/.gemrc
    sudo gem install extjs-mvc
## Do the tutorial
    cd workspace
    rails extonrails
    cd extonrails
    ln -s /www/shared/js/ext-3.0.1 public/javascripts/ext-3.0.1  here
    rm public/index.html